name: Miyaki Knot Dress
description:
This sexy and feminine fitted dress is a great alternative to the wrap dress. Made of soft lycra knit with printed japanese flowers, knotted at the waist, the dress drapes closely to the wearer at the right parts. Miyaki Knot Dress comes in sizes S, M, and L. This sexy dress also features:

- Knotted waist
- Fully Lined
- Sexy fitted silhouette

Material:
- 100% lycra knit
- Knit (lining)

Like us on facebook and see more views of this dress.
https://www.facebook.com/ragdoll.fanpage

Miyaki Knot Dress has been designed and made in Singapore.

name: Pretty Pleats Dress
description:
A light and comfy swiss cotton dress with printed small flowers. Cutting is unique with multiple paneled bodice, extending into many box pleats at the waist and finishing off clean at the hems. This dress has drew huge interest among our customers on Facebook. Pretty Pleats Dress comes in sizes S, M, and L. This sweet dress also features:

- Concealed back zipper closure
- Paneled bodice
- Pleated skirt
- Fully Lined

Material:
- 100% printed swiss cotton
- Acetate (lining)

Like us on facebook and see more views of this dress.
https://www.facebook.com/ragdoll.fanpage

Pretty Pleats Dress has been designed and made in Singapore.
